Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Example 4",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "   The c.d.f. is sometimes a better device for getting a handle on the \
distribution of a random variable than the p.m.f.  For instance, remember \
that in Chapter 1 we simulated random samples, for each of which we \
calculated a maximum or minimum sample value.  We then used a list of such \
extrema to give a histogram of their empirical distributions.  Here we will \
find the exact theoretical distribution of a maximum sample value. \n\t\
Suppose that the random experiment is to draw five numbers randomly in \
sequence and with replacement from ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"1", ",", "2", ",", "...", ",", "20"}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]]],
 ".  Let ",
 StyleBox["X",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " be the maximum of the sample values, e.g., if  \[Omega] = {5, 2, 10, 4, \
15} then ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"X", 
     RowBox[{"(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "=", "15"}], TraditionalForm]]],
 ".  Though it is not clear immediately what is the p.m.f. of ",
 StyleBox["X",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", we can compute the c.d.f. easily.  In order for the largest observation ",
 StyleBox["X",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " to be less than or equal to a number ",
 StyleBox["x",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", all five sample values (call them ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["X", "1"], ",", 
    SubscriptBox["X", "2"], ",", 
    SubscriptBox["X", "3"], ",", 
    SubscriptBox["X", "4"], ",", 
    SubscriptBox["X", "5"]}], TraditionalForm]]],
 ") must be less than or equal to ",
 StyleBox["x",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ".  Since sampling is done with replacement, we may assume that the five \
sample values are mutually independent; hence, for ",
 StyleBox["x",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " \[Element] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"1", ",", "2", ",", "...", ",", "20"}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]]],
 ","
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.4359669630425177`*^9, 3.4359669630485177`*^9}, {
   3.4361136817609997`*^9, 3.436113692435*^9}, 3.4564953351476*^9}],

